| TC-T3.7 | assign_model_ids migrates tier to model_id | ✅ verified |
| TC-T3.8 | assign_model_ids falls back to first model when tier not found | ✅ verified |
| TC-T3.9 | assign_model_ids skips configs that already have model_id | ✅ verified |
| TC-T3.10 | assign_model_ids handles empty api_sources | ✅ verified |
| TC-T3.11 | Serde round-trip — old JSON (no model_id) deserializes with defaults | ✅ verified |
